OL,3,CRising costs and restrictions threaten
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland's fishing industry
OL,6,FFishermen have told UTV that a crisis
OL,7,Ffacing Northern Ireland's fishing
OL,8,Findustry is costing them their
OL,9,Flivelihoods due to soaring fuel prices
OL,10,Fand restrictions on where they can
OL,11,Foperate.
OL,13,FConcerns around working visas have
OL,14,Falso been raised at a meeting with the
OL,15,FSecretary of State in Kilkeel.
OL,17,FIt is estimated that around 70% of
OL,18,Fworkers on fleets, which are operating
OL,19,Fout of fishing ports in Northern
OL,20,FIreland, are from overseas.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
