CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775146264
OL,3,CRising costs and restrictions threaten
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland's fishing industry
OL,6,F"From 50p a litre to #1.28 a
OL,7,Flitre`it's a massive jump. The crew
OL,8,Fonly gets paid from what is left over
OL,9,Ffrom the catch after all the
OL,10,Fexpenses," said fisherman Kenneth
OL,11,FPatterson.
OL,13,FThe harbour he operates out of was
OL,14,Fonce thriving.JKilkeel even hosted a
OL,15,Fdedicated festival for prawns back in
OL,16,Fthe 1960s.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
