PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775146264
OL,3,CRising costs and restrictions threaten
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland's fishing industry
OL,6,FFuel prices due to the Middle East
OL,7,Fconflict, concerns about the cost of
OL,8,Fskilled visas for foreign workers and
OL,9,Fa new fishing exclusion zone set by
OL,10,Fthe Isle of Man government are the
OL,11,Flatest challenges he and others are
OL,12,Fnow caught up in.
OL,14,FThe Isle of Man's new rules mean
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland boats with workers
OL,16,Fholding skilled worker or transit
OL,17,Fvisas, cannot operate within 12
OL,18,Fnatuical miles of its coastline.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
