FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775146264
OL,3,CRising costs and restrictions threaten
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland's fishing industry
OL,6,FIt was just one of the issues heard
OL,7,Fduring a meeting with fishermen in
OL,8,FKilkeel.
OL,10,F"These times are tough. There is a
OL,11,Fconflict in the Gulf and the sooner
OL,12,Fthat comes to an end, the sooner we
OL,13,Fcan see those fuel prices come down,"
OL,14,Fsaid Hilary Benn MP, Secretary of
OL,15,FState.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
