PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775146264
OL,3,CRising costs and restrictions threaten
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland's fishing industry
OL,6,F"We've also been discussing the
OL,7,Fchallenges of crewing the boats. At
OL,8,Fthe moment, there's the seasonal
OL,9,Fworkers visa that comes to an end at
OL,10,Fthe end of the year, and I'm going to
OL,11,Fgo and talk to my home office
OL,12,Fcolleagues about that."
OL,14,FStormont's Environment Minister, who
OL,15,Fwas also there, is due to meet with
OL,16,Fhis Manx counterparts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
