CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775146264
OL,3,CRising costs and restrictions threaten
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland's fishing industry
OL,6,F"The issue of special squeeze, whether
OL,7,Fit's regards to the decision for my
OL,8,Flayman or in relation to other issues,
OL,9,Fis a significant concern and it's
OL,10,Fimportant we work with the fishing
OL,11,Fcommunity to address those concerns
OL,12,Fand give them strong viability in the
OL,13,Ffuture ahead," said Andrew Muir MP,
OL,14,FEnvironment Minister.
